<p>[2] M. Granovetter and R. Soong, Threshold models of diffusion and collective behavior, J. Math. Sociol 9, 165 (1983).</p>

<p>[3] Z. Ruan, G. Iniguez, M. Karsai, and J. Kertesz, Kinetics of social contagion, Phys. Rev. Lett. 115, 218702 (2015).</p>

<p>[4] M. Karsai, G. Iniguez, R. Kikas, K. Kaski and J. Kertesz, Local cascades induced global contagion: How heterogeneous thresholds, exogenous effects, and unconcerned behavior govern online adoption spreading. Sci. Rep. 6, 27178 (2016).</p>
